WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.070
Lately, the Lord said, 'Brandon, I need you

00:00:02.080 --> 00:00:05.110
to encourage my people. I need you

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:08.390
to tell them about what's coming: about

00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:11.110
the glory, about the last outpouring,

00:00:11.110 --> 00:00:11.120
the

00:00:11.120 --> 00:00:14.990
Holy Ghost, miracle restoration, and

00:00:14.990 --> 00:00:15.000
revival.'I'm

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:16.550
excited to be with you all again

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:19.109
today. I have another video for you, of

00:00:19.119 --> 00:00:21.870
course. I told you all it's like

00:00:21.880 --> 00:00:24.509
looking at a thin quarter or whatever

00:00:24.519 --> 00:00:27.630
you have in your country—a coin. You can

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.150
either focus on the dark or you can

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:33.110
focus on the light. It's like

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:35.150
two sides of a

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:37.630
coin: the darkness is going to get darker in

00:00:37.640 --> 00:00:40.029
these last days with the birthing pains,

00:00:40.039 --> 00:00:42.270
but the Lord told me the light is going

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:44.029
to start getting lighter.

00:00:44.039 --> 00:00:47.069
You can see it; it'll be tangible.

00:00:47.079 --> 00:00:50.830
The last outpouring, a great harvest of

00:00:50.840 --> 00:00:53.430
souls, is what's about to happen. We're

00:00:53.440 --> 00:00:56.430
about to see one of the greatest

00:00:56.440 --> 00:01:00.590
things, like Bible times, like when

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:03.910
Moses parted the Red Sea and walked

00:01:03.920 --> 00:01:07.070
across dry land, the plagues, and

00:01:07.080 --> 00:01:09.749
all the things you know—seeing blinded

00:01:09.759 --> 00:01:12.830
eyes open, deaf ears pop open,

00:01:12.830 --> 00:01:12.840
and

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:15.230
autistic children completely delivered

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:18.190
and set free by the power of God. We're

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:21.109
about to see those things.

00:01:21.119 --> 00:01:23.030
If the Bible were still being written today,

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:25.830
we would be part of the

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:28.550
next chapter. I truly believe it

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:31.390
with all my heart; that's how amazing

00:01:31.400 --> 00:01:33.590
these miracles are going to be. I believe

00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:35.350
with all my heart

00:01:35.350 --> 00:01:35.360
that

00:01:35.360 --> 00:01:37.190
people will be translating from one place to

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:38.990
another, going and preaching the gospel.

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:41.710
You may be in a city in America and

00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:44.270
all of a sudden you're in Africa, Asia, Australia, or

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:51.270
South

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:53.429
America. I believe those are the kinds of

00:01:53.439 --> 00:01:55.310
things we're going to start to

00:01:55.310 --> 00:01:55.320
see—the

00:01:55.320 --> 00:01:59.109
glory of God. These testimonies

00:01:59.119 --> 00:02:01.830
that I'm about to show you, that Sister Billye

00:02:01.830 --> 00:02:01.840
here—she

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:04.190
read off a bunch of

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:06.749
prophecies that Brother Hagin gave from

00:02:06.759 --> 00:02:09.749
the '80s and the '70s and right

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:12.470
before he went home, about the last

00:02:12.480 --> 00:02:15.309
outpouring, about the glorious church

00:02:15.319 --> 00:02:18.229
rising up and being what we were called

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:22.790
to be. This one was given

00:02:22.790 --> 00:02:22.800
in

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:26.150
1980: 'We're right on the verge of

00:02:26.160 --> 00:02:28.350
the greatest move and manifestation of

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:30.670
the spirit of God this world has

00:02:30.680 --> 00:02:33.750
ever seen. Praise God, here we go.'And if

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:35.790
you'll give the more earnest heed

00:02:35.790 --> 00:02:35.800
unto

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:37.630
these things which you have

00:02:37.630 --> 00:02:37.640
heard—so

00:02:37.640 --> 00:02:39.830
think about, this was back in 1980 about

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:42.470
faith and healing—but those things which

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:46.270
you've heard about the Holy Spirit, about

00:02:46.280 --> 00:02:48.949
angels, about divine

00:02:48.959 --> 00:02:52.949
visitations, about visions and

00:02:52.959 --> 00:02:55.589
dreams. 'And upon my handmaidens I'll pour

00:02:55.599 --> 00:02:57.630
out my spirit and they'll prophesy; my

00:02:57.640 --> 00:02:59.350
young men will prophesy, the young women

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:01.670
will prophesy.'The anointing and

00:03:01.680 --> 00:03:03.390
the outflow of the spirit of God shall

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:06.149
be great and amazing in these

00:03:06.159 --> 00:03:09.710
days, and there shall be visitations of

00:03:09.720 --> 00:03:12.750
angels. He goes on to speak about the

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:15.470
glory of the Lord and the cloud of glory.

00:03:15.480 --> 00:03:18.070
Praise God!

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:21.350
Gloria likes this part so much; it's one

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:23.430
of her favorite prophecies from Brother

00:03:23.430 --> 00:03:23.440
Hagin.

00:03:23.440 --> 00:03:26.550
'You will flow in the supernatural

00:03:26.560 --> 00:03:30.070
as your mind will be changed.'Praise God!

00:03:30.080 --> 00:03:32.990
I renew mine now; I didn't catch that

00:03:33.000 --> 00:03:34.589
part before,

00:03:34.599 --> 00:03:38.429
Gloria. 'Your heart shall be prepared and

00:03:38.439 --> 00:03:40.670
your mind will be

00:03:40.680 --> 00:03:45.470
changed until you will flow in the

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:48.270
supernatural as naturally as a bird

00:03:48.280 --> 00:03:50.910
flies in the

00:03:50.920 --> 00:03:54.710
air. You will flow in the

00:03:59.159 --> 00:04:02.309
supernatural as

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:06.429
naturally as a fish will swim in water. You will flow in the supernatural as naturally as you breathe the very

00:04:06.429 --> 00:04:06.439
air.'Praise

00:04:06.439 --> 00:04:07.990
God! 'You will not be conscious of

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:10.270
your faith; you'll not be conscious of

00:04:10.280 --> 00:04:12.789
what's going on around you, but rather

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:14.949
you'll be more conscious of the flow of

00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:17.710
the spirit of God. He will manifest

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:20.310
himself and he will accomplish that

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:22.350
which he desires for you. See, these are

00:04:22.360 --> 00:04:23.430
the last

00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:26.990
days and this is the end time.'Thank you,

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:29.830
Jesus! 'And you shall walk, and you shall

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:33.629
run, and you shall fly.'Praise God,

00:04:33.639 --> 00:04:36.469
literally and spiritually

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:38.870
speaking!

00:04:38.880 --> 00:04:42.110
Hallelujah! I chose

00:04:42.120 --> 00:04:43.469
some other

00:04:43.479 --> 00:04:46.710
ones because I want you to

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:49.870
see this one given in

00:04:49.880 --> 00:04:53.270
2002. The Lord told us what to do to

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:54.510
get

00:04:54.520 --> 00:04:58.550
it.

00:05:06.039 --> 00:05:09.749
'We are just about to enter into

00:05:09.759 --> 00:05:12.029
an area in the realm of the spirit in

00:05:12.039 --> 00:05:14.990
which only a few of us have touched, but

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:16.629
it will be

00:05:16.629 --> 00:05:16.639
widespread.'Thank

00:05:16.639 --> 00:05:18.909
you, Jesus! 'And all whose

00:05:18.919 --> 00:05:20.909
hearts are open, and whose minds are

00:05:20.919 --> 00:05:24.270
clear, and who are sincere and

00:05:24.270 --> 00:05:24.280
honest—those

00:05:24.280 --> 00:05:26.430
are the ones that will move

00:05:26.440 --> 00:05:30.309
in. For a great cloud of glory

00:05:30.319 --> 00:05:33.909
is hanging just over our

00:05:33.909 --> 00:05:33.919
heads.'Praise

00:05:33.919 --> 00:05:37.950
God! 'And that cloud will burst into a

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:41.590
torrent of outflow of the rain of the

00:05:41.590 --> 00:05:41.600
spirit.'That's

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:44.710
what you saw,

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:47.590
Lucy. 'And the power of God shall not only

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:50.990
be in us but rest upon us, and the plan

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.430
and the purpose of God shall be

00:05:53.440 --> 00:05:56.070
consummated.'God

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:59.110
has a plan! Not only for your

00:05:59.120 --> 00:06:00.749
life and mine, not only for your

00:06:00.759 --> 00:06:03.390
church and my ministry, but God has a

00:06:03.400 --> 00:06:05.550
plan for the last

00:06:05.560 --> 00:06:09.830
days. Be honest, sincere, and

00:06:09.830 --> 00:06:09.840
determined.

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:13.670
'I'm walking and will walk in his plan

00:06:13.680 --> 00:06:15.589
and fulfill his

00:06:15.599 --> 00:06:20.110
purpose, for these are the last

00:06:20.110 --> 00:06:20.120
days.'It's

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:22.589
time for us to change our

00:06:22.599 --> 00:06:25.070
thinking in some areas. It's time for us

00:06:25.080 --> 00:06:27.350
to listen to our hearts and listen to

00:06:27.360 --> 00:06:30.790
our spirits for counsel.

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:33.309
'I need counseling! Can you counsel

00:06:33.309 --> 00:06:33.319
me?'You

00:06:33.319 --> 00:06:35.710
have a counselor on the inside of you,

00:06:35.720 --> 00:06:38.029
the Holy Spirit, and he will counsel with

00:06:38.039 --> 00:06:40.749
you. He will talk to you; he will talk

00:06:40.759 --> 00:06:42.830
with you. He will instruct you; he will

00:06:42.840 --> 00:06:45.110
show you just what to do, and you'll be

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:47.270
glad. And the plan of God will be

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:49.749
consummated and the end shall come.

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:52.070
The dead in Christ shall rise, and we

00:06:52.080 --> 00:06:53.589
which are alive and remain will be

00:06:53.599 --> 00:06:55.909
caught up together to meet the

00:06:55.919 --> 00:06:58.749
Lord in the air, and so shall we ever be

00:06:58.759 --> 00:07:01.430
with the Lord. So rejoice and be glad!

00:07:01.440 --> 00:07:04.309
Praise God! Now, this one: 'There will be a

00:07:04.319 --> 00:07:05.830
revival of the

00:07:05.830 --> 00:07:05.840
supernatural—not

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:08.070
only the supernatural

00:07:08.080 --> 00:07:10.830
in casting out devils, not only the

00:07:10.840 --> 00:07:13.629
supernatural in healing the sick, not

00:07:13.639 --> 00:07:15.510
only the supernatural in speaking with

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:17.350
other tongues, but the supernatural in

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:19.070
the seen

00:07:19.080 --> 00:07:22.869
realm. Men will see the glory of God. A

00:07:22.879 --> 00:07:24.390
cloud will hang over certain

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:26.589
congregations, even the church buildings,

00:07:26.599 --> 00:07:29.390
for days at a

00:07:29.390 --> 00:07:29.400
time.'And

00:07:29.400 --> 00:07:31.670
everybody who passes by—sinner and saint

00:07:31.670 --> 00:07:31.680
alike—will

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:33.830
say,

00:07:33.840 --> 00:07:36.710
'What in the world is that?

00:07:36.720 --> 00:07:39.150
I've never seen anything like

00:07:39.150 --> 00:07:39.160
that!'And

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:40.589
there will be in other places

00:07:40.589 --> 00:07:40.599
the

00:07:40.599 --> 00:07:42.430
fire of the

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:45.230
spirit that will actually become

00:07:45.240 --> 00:07:47.790
literal. In the spirit realm, some

00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:50.149
of us have seen it;

00:07:50.159 --> 00:07:52.350
we've been conscious of the fire of God,

00:07:52.360 --> 00:07:54.309
but the fire will actually come into

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:56.350
manifestation. There will be people,

00:07:56.360 --> 00:07:58.670
sinners as well as saints, that will see

00:07:58.680 --> 00:08:00.309
fire over the heads of the

00:08:00.319 --> 00:08:02.670
people. There will be people driving

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:04.469
down the street or down the highway and

00:08:04.479 --> 00:08:06.270
they'll see fire on the tops of the

00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:08.430
buildings, and they will come and say,

00:08:08.440 --> 00:08:11.510
'What does all this mean?'But

00:08:11.510 --> 00:08:11.520
you see—now

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:15.790
get this—the Lord will use signs of his

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:20.309
presence to bring people in in the last

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:22.230
days. That's how we're going to get

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:23.550
the harvest right

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:25.909
there. The outpouring of the spirit is

00:08:25.919 --> 00:08:28.589
going to draw them in. 'I will use signs of

00:08:28.599 --> 00:08:30.029
his

00:08:30.039 --> 00:08:33.589
to bring people in in the last

00:08:33.589 --> 00:08:33.599
days.'Praise

00:08:33.599 --> 00:08:36.230
the Lord! Men and women too will

00:08:36.240 --> 00:08:39.670
be transported

00:08:39.680 --> 00:08:42.110
like Philip was and found in

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:44.829
another place. And great

00:08:44.839 --> 00:08:46.509
shall be the reward

00:08:46.519 --> 00:08:49.310
thereof, for the Lord God is the same

00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:52.110
today as he was yesterday. His power has

00:08:52.120 --> 00:08:54.230
not diminished and his name is still the

00:08:54.240 --> 00:08:56.829
same today. He can make the iron ax head

00:08:56.839 --> 00:08:59.350
float today; he can divide the river just

00:08:59.360 --> 00:09:01.190
for two men to cross over

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:03.829
today; he can feed five thousand with a little

00:09:03.839 --> 00:09:08.829
boy's lunch. He is the miracle-working God!

00:09:08.839 --> 00:09:10.269
Yes, this is what I've been looking for

00:09:10.279 --> 00:09:13.829
lately: the instruction. What do we do?

00:09:13.839 --> 00:09:18.630
Listen: 'Brag on him.'Praise the

00:09:18.640 --> 00:09:21.150
Lord! Brag on

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:27.430
him, lift him up, draw attention unto him,

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:30.350
tell about how great he

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:34.110
is. How awesome is our God! Lord, do that

00:09:34.120 --> 00:09:36.509
tonight: get up in

00:09:36.519 --> 00:09:39.509
faith and tell what great things he's

00:09:39.519 --> 00:09:42.269
going to do. He's going to do

00:09:42.279 --> 00:09:45.990
it, and we're going to see it! Hallelujah!

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:48.069
'For the purpose of it all is that you

00:09:48.079 --> 00:09:50.230
may be fishers of men.

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:55.310
Quit fishing in your own

00:09:55.320 --> 00:09:57.750
bathtubs; there are not any fish in your

00:09:57.760 --> 00:10:00.550
own bathtub! Go out where the

00:10:00.550 --> 00:10:00.560
fish

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:03.790
are and throw out the nets—not the hook,

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:06.949
the nets—and pull them in!'Hallelujah! And

00:10:06.959 --> 00:10:09.829
bring them in, and the glory of the Lord

00:10:09.839 --> 00:10:11.269
shall

00:10:11.279 --> 00:10:15.110
shine, and the end time shall come, and

00:10:15.120 --> 00:10:17.230
he's going in the Holy Ghost. He's been

00:10:17.240 --> 00:10:20.230
praying in the Holy Ghost, and he begins

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:23.829
to say

00:10:23.839 --> 00:10:26.750
this: 'Moving into that

00:10:26.760 --> 00:10:29.590
place is fueled by

00:10:29.600 --> 00:10:33.110
prayer. It's fueled by prayer, fired by

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:37.430
the Spirit, and ignited with His

00:10:37.430 --> 00:10:37.440
glory.'Wow,

00:10:37.440 --> 00:10:39.949
say that again. He got so

00:10:39.959 --> 00:10:41.150
tickled over saying that he started

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:43.150
saying, 'Hallelujah to Jesus, glory to

00:10:43.150 --> 00:10:43.160
God.'I

00:10:43.160 --> 00:10:44.829
said, 'Glory to God, glory to God,

00:10:44.829 --> 00:10:44.839
hallelujah.'Fueled

00:10:44.839 --> 00:10:46.829
by prayer. And he

00:10:46.839 --> 00:10:48.389
starts talking about it; he said, 'If

00:10:48.399 --> 00:10:50.670
there's no fuel, there's nothing to

00:10:50.670 --> 00:10:50.680
ignite.'He

00:10:50.680 --> 00:10:52.829
said, 'Notice what the Spirit

00:10:52.829 --> 00:10:52.839
said.'I

00:10:52.839 --> 00:10:54.710
never thought of it—it came

00:10:54.720 --> 00:10:56.269
out of the inside of me—he said, 'I never

00:10:56.279 --> 00:10:57.430
thought of it

00:10:57.440 --> 00:11:00.430
before: fueled by

00:11:00.440 --> 00:11:03.069
prayer, fired by the Spirit,

00:11:03.069 --> 00:11:03.079
and

00:11:03.079 --> 00:11:05.509
ignited with His

00:11:05.509 --> 00:11:05.519
glory.'We

00:11:05.519 --> 00:11:07.509
have to stop and analyze that.

00:11:07.519 --> 00:11:09.110
Then he comes to

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:12.829
this: 'If there is no fuel, there's

00:11:12.839 --> 00:11:13.829
nothing to

00:11:13.839 --> 00:11:16.590
fire. If there's no

00:11:16.600 --> 00:11:18.870
fuel, there's nothing to

00:11:18.880 --> 00:11:20.750
fire. It is

00:11:20.760 --> 00:11:26.509
fueled by

00:11:26.509 --> 00:11:26.519
prayer.'We've

00:11:26.519 --> 00:11:30.230
got a big key here:

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:33.870
prayer. All this praying in the Spirit,

00:11:33.880 --> 00:11:35.350
the Holy Ghost

00:11:35.360 --> 00:11:38.310
said, is going to be

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:40.190
fueled by

00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:42.750
prayer. There will be

00:11:42.760 --> 00:11:45.190
churches in the body of Christ, in

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:47.910
buildings where they meet, where the

00:11:47.920 --> 00:11:50.030
glory of God will fill the place like a

00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:53.310
cloud and everybody will see it. And

00:11:53.320 --> 00:11:55.350
when that glory comes in manifestation,

00:11:55.360 --> 00:11:57.230
people walking by and driving by in

00:11:57.240 --> 00:11:59.150
their cars, even the unsaved, will

00:11:59.160 --> 00:12:02.190
feel the power; and folks down at the end

00:12:02.200 --> 00:12:03.949
of the block will fall under the power

00:12:03.959 --> 00:12:05.710
in their homes. Thank You, Father. And they

00:12:05.710 --> 00:12:05.720
will

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:07.990
wonder, 'What is this strange power that's

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:10.710
in manifestation for the glory of

00:12:10.710 --> 00:12:10.720
God?'And

00:12:10.720 --> 00:12:13.069
the power of God will, like a cloud,

00:12:13.079 --> 00:12:16.750
hang over whole cities because you

00:12:17.949 --> 00:12:17.959
prayed—because

00:12:23.399 --> 00:12:27.629
you believed. I just want

00:12:27.639 --> 00:12:30.110
to do a recap here. So, here we are.

00:12:30.120 --> 00:12:32.670
She's talking about how we're going to

00:12:32.680 --> 00:12:36.230
fuel this end-time revival, how we get

00:12:36.240 --> 00:12:37.030
the

00:12:37.040 --> 00:12:39.069
manifestation of what we're believing

00:12:39.079 --> 00:12:42.430
for instead of just waiting for it to

00:12:42.440 --> 00:12:45.189
happen. I know it's in God's timing, but

00:12:45.199 --> 00:12:46.990
just like Brother Hagin was talking

00:12:47.000 --> 00:12:51.189
about it, prayer is a major key to

00:12:51.199 --> 00:12:55.829
this, interceding for the last

00:12:55.839 --> 00:12:58.189
outpouring. Just like it was—you know, if

00:12:58.199 --> 00:13:00.350
we go back to what John

00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:03.910
Kilpatrick said with the Pensacola

00:13:03.910 --> 00:13:03.920
Revival—they

00:13:03.920 --> 00:13:07.430
had prayer there

00:13:07.440 --> 00:13:10.550
every night for a while, and they

00:13:10.560 --> 00:13:11.990
prayed

00:13:11.990 --> 00:13:12.000
for

00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.829
two

00:13:13.839 --> 00:13:17.710
years for a revival to break out in

00:13:17.720 --> 00:13:21.710
that area. And so it was birthed

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:24.150
through

00:13:24.160 --> 00:13:27.150
intercessory prayer, continually praying

00:13:27.160 --> 00:13:29.189
in the Spirit. That church

00:13:29.199 --> 00:13:32.509
prayed and prayed, and

00:13:32.519 --> 00:13:37.310
then on a Father's Day, the

00:13:37.320 --> 00:13:39.870
manifestation of the

00:13:39.880 --> 00:13:42.310
outpouring started to manifest and took

00:13:42.320 --> 00:13:45.629
place. It came. At its very start, there were

00:13:45.639 --> 00:13:48.110
three men: George

00:13:48.110 --> 00:13:48.120
Whitefield,

00:13:48.120 --> 00:13:50.790
John Wesley,

00:13:50.800 --> 00:13:52.990
and Charles Wesley—three

00:13:52.990 --> 00:13:53.000
Englishmen—and

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:55.990
they formed a club called

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:59.110
The Holy Club. In their

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:00.150
Holy

00:14:00.160 --> 00:14:04.030
Club, they endeavored to live a holy life

00:14:04.040 --> 00:14:09.069
and to pray. Their Holy Club had

00:14:09.079 --> 00:14:13.230
an unusual thing that happened to

00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:16.069
it. I shall read you about it right here.

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:18.749
I wonder what book that is. It

00:14:18.759 --> 00:14:20.790
had grown to 32

00:14:20.800 --> 00:14:24.110
members

00:14:24.120 --> 00:14:27.310
when there came—just think about

00:14:27.320 --> 00:14:29.030
that right there. Sorry to interrupt

00:14:29.040 --> 00:14:32.870
again, but 32 people praying, that's all.

00:14:32.880 --> 00:14:35.550
Whenever I do a prayer thing on here,

00:14:35.560 --> 00:14:40.629
we'll have 3,500 people pray in

00:14:40.639 --> 00:14:43.310
the Spirit for at least 15 minutes. So

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:46.829
just think about that; we have great

00:14:46.839 --> 00:14:50.110
power and unity in prayer. So,

00:14:50.110 --> 00:14:50.120
thirty-some

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:53.710
people here. Upon them, a great outpouring

00:14:53.720 --> 00:14:57.310
of the Spirit on New Year's Day,

00:14:57.320 --> 00:15:00.629
1739. Over 60 people were present at that

00:15:00.639 --> 00:15:03.629
moment when the Wesleys, George

00:15:03.629 --> 00:15:03.639
Whitefield,

00:15:03.639 --> 00:15:06.150
and others received God's power in the

00:15:06.160 --> 00:15:09.350
Spirit. Waves of unspeakable joy passed

00:15:09.360 --> 00:15:11.590
over them, and they prostrated themselves

00:15:11.600 --> 00:15:14.550
on the ground in awe and adoration. Thank

00:15:14.560 --> 00:15:16.550
God. It gave these men a deep conviction

00:15:16.560 --> 00:15:18.430
that He was about to do something great

00:15:18.440 --> 00:15:21.389
and wonderful in England. And as

00:15:21.399 --> 00:15:24.949
this great revival

00:15:24.959 --> 00:15:27.590
moved, it brought them to

00:15:27.600 --> 00:15:30.350
America. It moved in the English-speaking

00:15:30.360 --> 00:15:32.269
world. There are chapters in

00:15:32.269 --> 00:15:32.279
here—Paul

00:15:32.279 --> 00:15:33.990
Brady, where are you?—about how it moved

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:36.309
to Ulster and how it moved to

00:15:36.319 --> 00:15:38.629
Belfast and the things that happened. But

00:15:38.639 --> 00:15:41.150
in the United States of America, it

00:15:41.160 --> 00:15:44.150
became known as the Great Awakening. It

00:15:44.160 --> 00:15:45.710
was from

00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:51.670
1739

00:15:51.680 --> 00:15:53.230
until

00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:56.150
1791. There was a great connection

00:15:56.160 --> 00:15:58.550
between the Great Awakening and the

00:15:58.560 --> 00:16:01.870
American

00:16:01.880 --> 00:16:04.629
Revolution. The

00:16:04.629 --> 00:16:04.639
outcome

00:16:04.639 --> 00:16:07.590
of the Great

00:16:07.600 --> 00:16:14.150
Awakening was the United States of

00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:16.870
America. And one of the leaders—and these

00:16:16.880 --> 00:16:18.990
things are all in this book

00:16:19.000 --> 00:16:22.470
right

00:16:22.470 --> 00:16:22.480
here—was

00:16:22.480 --> 00:16:25.790
greatly affected by a man named

00:16:25.790 --> 00:16:25.800
Finney.

00:16:25.800 --> 00:16:26.829
The

00:16:26.829 --> 00:16:26.839
Finney

00:16:26.839 --> 00:16:29.749
revivals. And there's so much clue in

00:16:29.759 --> 00:16:33.509
here as to what happened with

00:16:33.509 --> 00:16:33.519
Finney,

00:16:33.519 --> 00:16:35.550
and I want to read you just a little bit

00:16:35.560 --> 00:16:40.710
of it. Bless the Lord,

00:16:40.720 --> 00:16:44.150
hallelujah. Revival fires follow

00:16:44.150 --> 00:16:44.160
Finney.

00:16:44.160 --> 00:16:47.350
His

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:50.870
biographer said that perhaps the most

00:16:50.880 --> 00:16:52.910
remarkable account of the manifestations

00:16:52.920 --> 00:16:54.670
of the Holy Spirit's power since

00:16:54.680 --> 00:16:58.749
apostolic days was in Finney's meetings.

00:16:58.759 --> 00:17:00.629
It is crowded with accounts of spiritual

00:17:00.639 --> 00:17:02.870
outpourings which remind one of the Day

00:17:02.880 --> 00:17:05.669
of Pentecost. The intensity and

00:17:05.669 --> 00:17:05.679
constancy

00:17:05.679 --> 00:17:07.669
of his ardor were surprising. The sacred

00:17:07.679 --> 00:17:12.110
fire never seemed to burn low.

00:17:12.120 --> 00:17:15.270
His campaign, which began in New York

00:17:15.280 --> 00:17:18.230
State, was absolutely preparing the

00:17:18.240 --> 00:17:20.150
way for the mighty move of revival that

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:24.350
swept America in 1857 and

00:17:24.360 --> 00:17:27.069
1858. More than a million people came

00:17:27.079 --> 00:17:28.909
into the kingdom of God under his

00:17:28.919 --> 00:17:30.909
ministry, and though the population was not so

00:17:30.909 --> 00:17:30.919
large,

00:17:30.919 --> 00:17:34.430
85% of the professed converts

00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:36.710
in the Finney revivals remained true to

00:17:36.720 --> 00:17:39.470
God. These revivals spread and

00:17:39.470 --> 00:17:39.480
blessed

00:17:39.480 --> 00:17:41.990
churches from city to city and around

00:17:42.000 --> 00:17:46.590
and across America. God poured—in the

00:17:46.600 --> 00:17:48.430
early days of his walk with the Lord,

00:17:48.430 --> 00:17:48.440
Finney

00:17:48.440 --> 00:17:50.630
learned about prevailing prayer

00:17:50.640 --> 00:17:53.510
and prayer burdens, and he would spend

00:17:53.510 --> 00:17:53.520
time

00:17:53.520 --> 00:17:55.750
in prayer, often going to the woods

00:17:55.760 --> 00:17:59.350
to be alone with God.

00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:02.110
God poured out a spirit of prayer

00:18:02.120 --> 00:18:05.230
upon other people who followed Finney and

00:18:05.240 --> 00:18:08.029
went with him. Much private prayer

00:18:08.039 --> 00:18:11.350
accompanied this revival. And so

00:18:11.350 --> 00:18:11.360
Finney

00:18:11.360 --> 00:18:13.909
began to preach. He went to a town in New

00:18:13.919 --> 00:18:16.390
York named Antwerp. He walked through the

00:18:16.400 --> 00:18:19.029
streets, he heard profanity, and he spent

00:18:19.039 --> 00:18:21.750
the rest of the day in prayer. And before

00:18:21.760 --> 00:18:25.789
a few days, most of its 2,250 citizens

00:18:25.799 --> 00:18:28.990
were converted. Wow.

00:18:29.000 --> 00:18:31.310
He visited a nearby village. In the first

00:18:31.320 --> 00:18:33.909
service, the schoolhouse was full. After

00:18:33.919 --> 00:18:35.750
15 minutes, the congregation began to

00:18:35.760 --> 00:18:38.230
fall from their seats. They fell in every

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:40.990
direction and cried for mercy. 'If I

00:18:40.990 --> 00:18:41.000
had

00:18:41.000 --> 00:18:42.630
had a sword in each hand, I could not

00:18:42.640 --> 00:18:44.350
have cut them all from their seats as

00:18:44.360 --> 00:18:46.909
fast as they fell,'he wrote. Indeed, nearly

00:18:46.919 --> 00:18:48.909
the whole congregation were either on

00:18:48.919 --> 00:18:52.029
their knees or prostrate. 'I think in less

00:18:52.039 --> 00:18:53.950
than two minutes from the first shock

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:56.350
that fell upon them, everyone prayed for

00:18:56.360 --> 00:18:58.669
himself who was able to pray at all. I, of

00:18:58.679 --> 00:19:01.190
course, was obliged to stop preaching, for

00:19:01.200 --> 00:19:03.710
no one any longer paid attention to

00:19:03.710 --> 00:19:03.720
me.'Do

00:19:03.720 --> 00:19:04.990
it

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:07.710
again, do it again, Lord. The meetings went

00:19:07.720 --> 00:19:09.909
on and on, and whole

00:19:09.919 --> 00:19:12.510
towns would get saved. He went to New

00:19:12.520 --> 00:19:15.510
York, Oneida County. God gave a prayer

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:18.669
burden on Friday. Sunday, God came in

00:19:18.679 --> 00:19:20.950
power at the church services.

00:19:20.950 --> 00:19:20.960
Finney

00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:22.990
prevailed in prayer and spoke in several

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:25.950
parts of the town. A Mrs. Harris had

00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:28.669
wrestled in prayer night and day. When

00:19:28.679 --> 00:19:31.390
she met Finney, she said, 'The Lord has come.

00:19:31.400 --> 00:19:33.029
This work will spread over all this

00:19:33.039 --> 00:19:35.549
region. A cloud of mercy overhangs us, and

00:19:35.559 --> 00:19:37.990
we shall see a great work of grace that

00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:40.549
has never yet been seen.'Finney said that

00:19:40.559 --> 00:19:42.950
Mrs. Harris's face had a most unearthly,

00:19:42.960 --> 00:19:45.029
heavenly glow that was plainly from

00:19:45.039 --> 00:19:47.590
Heaven. She had won a revival through

00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:49.950
prayer. Praise God, through prayer. And

00:19:49.960 --> 00:19:51.710
then after the revival fire burned in

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:53.549
the West for a while, it came to the town

00:19:53.559 --> 00:19:56.110
of Rome. God gripped the people with such

00:19:56.120 --> 00:19:58.070
Holy Spirit conviction, Finney was afraid

00:19:58.080 --> 00:19:59.669
that the people could not control their

00:19:59.679 --> 00:20:01.909
emotions. Finney led in prayer at the

00:20:01.919 --> 00:20:03.230
close of the meeting in a low,

00:20:03.240 --> 00:20:05.870
unemotional voice, trying to restrain the

00:20:05.880 --> 00:20:08.510
people who had begun to weep and sigh. He

00:20:08.520 --> 00:20:10.190
urged them to control their feelings and

00:20:10.200 --> 00:20:12.590
go home without speaking a word to

00:20:12.600 --> 00:20:14.669
anyone. The people obeyed, but their

00:20:14.679 --> 00:20:16.549
sighing and sobbing continued as they

00:20:16.559 --> 00:20:18.590
went down the street to their homes. At

00:20:18.600 --> 00:20:21.270
daybreak, the people began sending for

00:20:21.270 --> 00:20:21.280
Finney.

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:23.510
He spent the morning going from

00:20:23.520 --> 00:20:25.830
house to house to pray with the people.

00:20:25.840 --> 00:20:27.390
He finally announced a meeting for

00:20:27.400 --> 00:20:30.390
inquirers, and many more were

00:20:30.400 --> 00:20:32.750
convicted in the evening service. People

00:20:32.760 --> 00:20:34.549
were so overwhelmed by the Holy Spirit's

00:20:34.559 --> 00:20:36.630
conviction that he dismissed the service

00:20:36.640 --> 00:20:39.230
and asked the people to go home. Revival

00:20:39.240 --> 00:20:40.870
went on for twenty nights with a prayer

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:42.630
meeting once a day, a meeting for inquirers at

00:20:42.640 --> 00:20:44.230
another time, and

00:20:44.230 --> 00:20:44.240
ministers'meetings

00:20:44.240 --> 00:20:47.350
at night. Some people collapsed

00:20:47.360 --> 00:20:49.310
from conviction in the church services

00:20:49.320 --> 00:20:51.310
and some later in their own homes. It had

00:20:51.320 --> 00:20:54.230
become common across America that people, by and

00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:56.590
large, in great groups of cities,

00:20:56.600 --> 00:20:59.270
were not born again. He

00:20:59.270 --> 00:20:59.280
would

00:20:59.280 --> 00:21:01.310
go into these places and these

00:21:01.320 --> 00:21:03.310
things would happen. Three men spent a

00:21:03.320 --> 00:21:06.789
day drinking and condemning the revival

00:21:06.799 --> 00:21:09.909
until one of them fell down dead.

00:21:09.919 --> 00:21:12.070
Nearly all of the adult population of

00:21:12.080 --> 00:21:14.070
Rome, New York, was brought to

00:21:14.070 --> 00:21:14.080
Christ—lawyers,

00:21:14.080 --> 00:21:16.070
merchants, physicians, and town

00:21:16.080 --> 00:21:18.990
leaders. The ministers said, "So far as my

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:20.909
congregation is concerned, the Millennium

00:21:20.919 --> 00:21:23.310
has come."Everyone who came into the

00:21:23.320 --> 00:21:25.470
village felt an overwhelming sense of

00:21:25.480 --> 00:21:28.549
God's presence. The sheriff of Utica, New

00:21:28.559 --> 00:21:31.549
York, twenty miles away, came on business. He had

00:21:31.559 --> 00:21:33.510
laughed and mocked at the reports of the

00:21:33.520 --> 00:21:36.549
revival. As his sleigh crossed the canal

00:21:36.559 --> 00:21:38.870
one mile outside of Rome, an awesome

00:21:38.880 --> 00:21:40.990
feeling of the presence of God gripped

00:21:41.000 --> 00:21:43.390
him. The nearer to the village he came,

00:21:43.400 --> 00:21:45.310
the more powerfully he sensed God's

00:21:45.320 --> 00:21:47.510
presence. The sheriff found the people in

00:21:47.520 --> 00:21:50.390
the business establishments too overcome

00:21:50.400 --> 00:21:52.909
with the awe of God—so overcome they

00:21:52.919 --> 00:21:55.470
could hardly speak without trying to keep from

00:21:55.480 --> 00:21:57.510
weeping. The sheriff got up several times

00:21:57.520 --> 00:21:59.549
and went to the window. He hurried to

00:21:59.559 --> 00:22:01.510
complete his business and hastened back

00:22:01.520 --> 00:22:05.870
to Utica. Soon he was converted. Bless the

00:22:05.880 --> 00:22:08.590
Lord, Finney urged the people to pray to

00:22:08.600 --> 00:22:10.750
God earnestly. Now get this;

00:22:10.760 --> 00:22:13.230
here's one part I want to highlight:

00:22:13.230 --> 00:22:13.240
Finney

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:16.350
would go into a town and he would urge the

00:22:16.360 --> 00:22:18.510
people to pray to God earnestly and

00:22:18.520 --> 00:22:22.549
expectantly for the immediate

00:22:22.559 --> 00:22:25.269
outpouring of His Holy Spirit.

00:22:25.279 --> 00:22:26.909
He told them that if they united in

00:22:26.919 --> 00:22:28.830
prayer, they could get God's answer

00:22:28.840 --> 00:22:30.390
quicker than a letter could come from

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:33.590
Albany, the state's capital. Several men

00:22:33.600 --> 00:22:35.870
agreed to prove God in that way and

00:22:35.880 --> 00:22:37.750
their prayer was answered just that

00:22:37.760 --> 00:22:40.590
quickly. Finney wrote, "Indeed, the

00:22:40.600 --> 00:22:43.070
town was full of prayer. Go where you

00:22:43.080 --> 00:22:45.310
would, you heard the voice of prayer.

00:22:45.320 --> 00:22:46.990
Pass along the streets, if two or three

00:22:47.000 --> 00:22:48.350
Christians happened to be together, they

00:22:48.360 --> 00:22:50.669
were praying. Wherever they met, they

00:22:50.679 --> 00:22:52.789
prayed. Wherever there was a sinner

00:22:52.799 --> 00:22:55.029
unconverted, especially if he manifested

00:22:55.039 --> 00:22:57.350
any opposition, you'd find two or three

00:22:57.360 --> 00:22:58.990
brothers or sisters agreeing to

00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:02.390
make him a particular subject of

00:23:02.390 --> 00:23:02.400
prayer."Hallelujah!

00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:05.230
That's what we have to do. The sheriff

00:23:05.230 --> 00:23:05.240
of Utica,

00:23:05.240 --> 00:23:07.950
a new convert, went back to the

00:23:07.960 --> 00:23:10.390
boarding house where he boarded and began to

00:23:10.400 --> 00:23:13.230
pray for the hotel keeper. In

00:23:13.230 --> 00:23:13.240
Utica,

00:23:13.240 --> 00:23:15.350
the Holy Ghost fell. A divine

00:23:15.360 --> 00:23:17.110
influence seemed to pervade Utica and

00:23:17.120 --> 00:23:19.510
Rome during these revivals and turned

00:23:19.520 --> 00:23:22.750
the area into a zone of holiness. The

00:23:22.760 --> 00:23:25.029
same phenomenon was occurring along the

00:23:25.039 --> 00:23:27.470
whole eastern coast of the United

00:23:27.480 --> 00:23:31.230
States. During the 1858

00:23:31.230 --> 00:23:31.240
revival—which

00:23:31.240 --> 00:23:32.870
was a later one—the

00:23:32.870 --> 00:23:32.880
Oneida Presbytery

00:23:32.880 --> 00:23:36.230
met in

00:23:36.230 --> 00:23:36.240
Utica.

00:23:36.240 --> 00:23:39.549
An

00:23:39.559 --> 00:23:41.909
aged clergyman complained that

00:23:41.919 --> 00:23:44.110
everywhere he went in the town, people

00:23:44.120 --> 00:23:46.430
talked about prayer and revival. He got

00:23:46.440 --> 00:23:48.269
up in the presbytery meeting and made a

00:23:48.279 --> 00:23:50.830
violent speech against the revival. That

00:23:50.840 --> 00:23:53.310
night, many Christians prayed fervently

00:23:53.320 --> 00:23:55.190
that the revival would not be hindered

00:23:55.200 --> 00:23:57.269
by his speech. In the morning, this

00:23:57.279 --> 00:23:58.909
minister was found dead in his bed

00:23:58.919 --> 00:24:04.830
in the hotel.

00:24:04.840 --> 00:24:07.909
I've heard Brother Hagin prophesy

00:24:07.919 --> 00:24:10.430
that when this

00:24:10.440 --> 00:24:12.669
starts, there are going to be some people that are

00:24:12.679 --> 00:24:13.870
going

00:24:13.880 --> 00:24:17.510
to go on home, and he

00:24:17.520 --> 00:24:20.950
prophesied that there would be such

00:24:20.960 --> 00:24:25.669
judgments. I love this part about

00:24:25.679 --> 00:24:28.350
it: a Methodist church was formed in the

00:24:28.360 --> 00:24:31.149
town and then a Presbyterian

00:24:31.159 --> 00:24:34.590
church. When Finney would go to a town,

00:24:34.600 --> 00:24:37.510
